# adrone-hs.vim
Remaked [this](http://github.com/aiya000/adrone.vim).

adrone-hs.vim is diary plugin for vim.  
adrone-hs.vim respected TweetVim UI.

# Require
+ haskell-stack
    - example `# pacman -S haskell-stack`

# How to use this
```vim
call dein#add('aiya000/adrone-hs.vim')
```

```console
$ cd {/path/to/adrone-hs.vim}
$ cd adrone-hs
$ stack build
```
